        public static Nao getNao(java.lang.String ip,
                         int port)
        Factory Method for returning a Nao Objekt. The given Nao instance is singleton, so if you call this method again, the same Object is returned again and the ip and port parameters of the method are ignored.
        Parameters:
        ip - the ip adress
        port - the port
        Returns:
        a new Nao instance.
